com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services

Class ReadDebitMemoRequestsService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sap.cloud.sdk.s4hana.datamodel.odata.services.ReadDebitMemoRequestsService

  • public class ReadDebitMemoRequestsService
extends Object

    This service enables external applications to integrate withread methods for processing debit memo requests in SAP S/4HANA Cloud. It enables you to retrieve debit memo requests in an API call.

    Business Documentation

    Reference: SAP API Business Hub

    Details:

    OData Service:API_DEBIT_MEMO_REQUEST_SRV
    API Version:1
    Minimum ERP Version:1708
    Communication Scenario:Debit Memo Request Integration (SAP_COM_0159)
    Scope Items:Debit Memo Processing (1F1)
